    <section class="page-section callout">
      <h2>Why this topic matters</h2>
      <p>Most people use websites every day without seeing the systems underneath them. Learning the basics of web servers and HTTP makes web development feel less mysterious. It also helps explain why performance, security, and network design matter so much when building sites people actually want to use.</p>
